<p>I am making a Linked List of Integers </p>  <pre><code>LinkedList&lt;Integer&gt; l1 = new LinkedList&lt;Integer&gt;(); l1.add(1); l1.add(2); l1.add(3); </code></pre>  <p>I want to remove 2nd entry i.e 2 from my list, So I used</p>  <pre><code>l1.remove(2); </code></pre>  <p>But actually, I found 3rd entry i.e 3 was removed. So <code>remove(int index)</code> was run by Java but I wanted <code>remove(Object o)</code> to run.</p>  <p>How to use <code>remove(Object o)</code> here ?</p>